1709
00:54:33,701 --> 00:54:36,330
What we'll eat here for lunch with the students...

1710
00:54:36,331 --> 00:54:37,840
from Bupyeong Middle School and Bupyeong High School is...

1711
00:54:37,841 --> 00:54:40,001
