1718
00:55:00,521 --> 00:55:01,660
- Of course.
- Sure.

1719
00:55:01,661 --> 00:55:05,330
So we provide at least two portions of thin-sliced pork belly...

1720
00:55:05,331 --> 00:55:06,500
per student.

1721
00:55:06,501 --> 00:55:08,447
