00:55:49,511 --> 00:55:50,610
We are in big trouble.

1745
00:55:50,611 --> 00:55:52,781
(We are in big trouble.)

1746
00:55:52,881 --> 00:55:54,650
- Let's start.
- Okay.

1747
00:55:54,651 --> 00:55:56,651
(Meat Scholarship Quiz starts now.)

1748
00:55:56,781 --> 00:55:57,781
Let's leave the gas on.

1749
00:55:57,782 --> 00:55:59,297
You have to be smart to wrestle, right?

1750
00:55:59,321 --> 00:56:01,321
You have to figure out all the possible scenarios.

1751
00:56:01,351 --> 00:56:02,511
You have to calculate it all.

1752
00:56:03,121 --> 00:56:04,150
All right.

1753
00:56:04,151 --> 00:56:05,761
(Lunch is served.)

1754
00:56:06,321 --> 00:56:08,691
We can do the quiz after having this, yes?

1755
00:56:09,331 --> 00:56:11,230
